this.$debug
If debug is true, this will be the iQ object for the visible rectangle.
this._activeTab
The TabItem for the group’s active tab.
We keep track of whether the tabs are hidden in this (internal) variable so we still have access to that information during the window’s unload event, when window.Tabs no longer exists.

(boolean) Whether this trench is currently active or not.
(Range) the currently active range

For internal use only
